    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打败终极敌人！通过三个难度逐渐增加的关卡，躲避致命的攻击，消灭80%的方块，赢得胜利。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.poster.avif?t=1733854924\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.webm?t=1733854924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.mp4?t=1733854924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接史诗般的战斗，在 Tilebreaker Next Level 中拯救地球免受外星人入侵！ 外星人用黑暗、不可渗透的方块网络包围了地球，摧毁它们的任务就落在你的肩上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.poster.avif?t=1733854924\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.webm?t=1733854924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.mp4?t=1733854924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武装自己，准备好迎接快节奏的动作，躲避致命的敌人攻击，并在心跳加速的战斗中面对强大的外星老板。 随着您通过越来越具有挑战性的关卡，您将遇到复杂的攻击模式、更坚硬的方块和意想不到的障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.poster.avif?t=1733854924\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.webm?t=1733854924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.mp4?t=1733854924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与全球玩家竞争，以实现最快的完成时间并攀登排行榜。 你能进入前 5 名吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/406be1db32c9fa9d0e48ee02775f8a95.avif?t=1733854924\" width=610 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不会孤军奋战！ 控制你强大的英雄，留意有价值的强化道具，例如增加速度、伤害等。凭借快速的反应和战略思维，您将克服最艰巨的挑战，并更接近您的最终目标：摧毁方块的来源并恢复地球的光芒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276660/extras/7f08147fe5073ab3e89024f2ae916187.avif?t=1733854924\" width=610 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>您准备好加入战斗、拯救地球并体验不间断的动作了吗？ 让我们玩 Tilebreaker Next Level！</strong></h2>",
